The paper discusses a methodology for assessing national research performance in specific fields, which involves bibliometric analysis. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Digital Libraries (cs.DL) or Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper may also be relevant to the Cybersecurity (cs.CR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-categories, as these fields are also mentioned in the abstract. Finally, the paper may be relevant to the Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-category, as the methodology proposed involves analyzing scientific publications.
